com.handmark.pulltorefresh.library.internal

接口 EmptyViewMethodAccessor

  • 所有已知实现类:
    PullToRefreshListView.InternalListView

    public interface EmptyViewMethodAccessor
    Interface that allows PullToRefreshBase to hijack the call to AdapterView.setEmptyView()
    作者:
    chris

    • 方法概要

      方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void setEmptyView(android.view.View emptyView)
      Should call PullToRefreshBase.setEmptyView() which will then automatically call through to setEmptyViewInternal()
      void setEmptyViewInternal(android.view.View emptyView)
      Calls upto AdapterView.setEmptyView()
